snippet.title: The Warfront major content update is available now! | Bug Alliance #bugalliance #gameplay #gaming
snippet.description:
We are super excited to announce that Major Content Update - The Warfront is available now! New game mode, new bug character, new enemies and tons of other epic stuffs awaits you. Are you ready to stand against the worm horde in a new frontline?
#BugAlliance  #indiegame #actiongames #games #youtubegaming #teamyoutube
